{"tid":2245323,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"鄺葆賢渣男喻鄧炳強區會噍完鬆 妙解逐鄧令獲激讚：明知佢嚟傷你 仲畀佢傷？","createTime":"2020-10-16T06:38:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-16T08:12:08.000Z","uid":240362,"like":38,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"0b59e4d45f110348fb812cf20328df63e112ed00","tid":2245323,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:38:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/Fz1y_miFBdNJcU2dDDeoiAEfYZk=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ESYJB24GFJG6PFKCQIA7IXJNZQ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FFz1y_miFBdNJcU2dDDeoiAEfYZk%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FESYJB24GFJG6PFKCQIA7IXJNZQ.png&h=3c5aa504&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近年出席區議會的警方代表，被批評多次藐視由居民一人一票選出的區議員；無理反對區議會議程和開會文件、肆意缺席會議，即使出席也只自說自話，迴避議員提問，甚至擅離職守拉隊離場鬧情緒，卻在門外對傳媒侃侃而談。為遏止此等歪風，九龍城區議會近日不讓警務處處長鄧炳強到訪，鄧開記招反擊。副主席鄺葆賢在電台節目解釋「逐鄧令」時，以「渣男」比喻鄧，斥他只利用區議員做騷：「明知道佢嚟到都係會傷害你，你真係仲畀佢傷害咩？渣男嚟㗎嘛！」網民紛讚鄺的比喻一針見血。<br />\n<br />\n鄺葆賢日前已在Facebook隔空反駁鄧：「#真心想傾就唔會一直又ban文件又離席啦 #上次盧偉聰放人飛機就得」。她昨在商台指，鄧炳強早前在其他區議會的回應，「嚟嚟去去『三幅被』，淨係想借（區議會）個平台，講自己有幾咁正義，佢啲兄弟有幾咁熱血」，並非認真回答議員，甚至拉大隊在門外開記招，滿足自己對鏡頭慾望。被問到「逐鄧令」是否意味議員放棄質詢，鄺則大爆金句：「如果一個人傷害咗你好多次，明知道佢嚟到都係會傷害你，你真係仲畀佢傷害咩？渣男嚟㗎嘛！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/M6QUNOQMDFDYZP5WZPO6G2H2OA/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FM6QUNOQMDFDYZP5WZPO6G2H2OA%2F&d=Z58AETknIeTPCCdXMCOVU1YPZSwMlx1ag7qd%2FaAfmLs%3D&h=054ab980\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201016%2FM6QUNOQMDFDYZP5WZPO6G2H2OA%2F&h=337ecb0e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201016/M6QUNOQMDFDYZP5WZPO6G2H2OA/</a>"},{"pid":"26c5930a4805a853ae376f33ff95649622e5a051","tid":2245323,"uid":193077,"like":4,"dislike":8,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:44:30.000Z","msg":"who?"},{"pid":"2b866e83f25bd5e29f9d57906c858cacbc2589ea","tid":2245323,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c014782aa295a5d881afe637bd787dd00e974ec8","tid":2245323,"uid":11291,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:01:55.000Z","msg":"渣咩男<br />\n賤種就差唔多<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0210b7671671c365eb580bf3ce5d980160d66f6","tid":2245323,"uid":45910,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:03:11.000Z","msg":"炳強你條仆街俾阿葆抖下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8958317fc86e2c9f3a9d6e5ffe9a5cf374fc21f0","tid":2245323,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2b866e83f25bd5e29f9d57906c858cacbc2589ea","tid":2245323,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T06:48:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-16T07:03:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a282a8047d85b7fe27102d05fc7a23b649a0a2a3","tid":